"Run a regression test, and compare the contents of the window against "
"against a valid image.  This will use arguments from sys.argv to set the "
"testing options via the vtkTesting class, run the test script, and then call "
"vtkTesting.RegressionTest() to validate the image.  The return value will "
"the one provided by vtkTesting.RegressionTest()."
